+ * in the same order, any "after" callbacks implemented by {@code Extension1}
+ * are guaranteed to execute after any "after" callbacks implemented by
+ * {@code Extension2}. {@code Extension1} is therefore said to <em>wrap</em>
+ * {@code Extension2}.
